### **Project Overview**

Are you a nap enthusiast? A snooze connoisseur? Or just someone who‚Äôs mastered the art of sleeping in the weirdest corners of campus? Fear not, weary scholar‚Äîwe‚Äôve got you covered.

Our project is a **multimedia, Python-powered sleep rating system** designed to track, rate, and gamify sleeping habits across campus. It combines **personality quizzes**, **interactive QR codes**, **randomly cryptic quotes**, and **achievements for the elite nappers**. Basically, it‚Äôs like Pok√©mon, but instead of catching monsters, you catch Zs.

