### **It‚Äôs Not Just About the Code**

We want to **push boundaries**:

- Experiment with interactive multimedia.
- Learn from bugs (yes, we know there will be crashes when too many students scan at once).
- Make something **both elegant and ridiculous**, meaningful yet functional‚Äîbasically the perfect embodiment of college life.

